item.title: Get to Know Me. Morgan Sprouse
item.description:
Get to Know Me. Morgan Sprouse

 I play music which means I play the guitar, the bass, keys, and I think I can hold a beat. I'm also a big media fanatic, which means I like to make videos, shoot photos, and talk about everything I don't like. You can consider my hobby to be my atsprouse.vsco.co grid. The last thing I am is a marketer. I'm a senior marketing student at Oral Roberts University. And I'm very good. I lead my team to get "A"'s every time and my marketing professors love me.
